<br>
Thanks! Happy hunting. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uezno.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ezno</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/posticons/eyes.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 385<br> <font color=#333333>(4/7/01 8:19:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where should a level 12 mage hunt?</span><hr size=1> <br>
I've always liked hunting in E.Karana because it is not as crowded as places like the Oasis and there is the Gorge and EK right there to give variety.<br>
<br>
Wisps/YoungKodiaks in West Commons are also good. <p> <br>
<b>Ez</b> <br>
<i>"Good... Bad... I'm the guy with the fire elemental."</i><br><i>"Shop Smart. Shop Ez-Mart!"</i><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukjeldon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kjeldon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#333333>(4/8/01 2:12:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   For me</span><hr size=1> At level 12 I hunted NK Griffawns, when I hit the high teens I hunted Crags in EK. Right now Im doing Picklaw Goblins in HHK!<br>
